 After his initial surprise and shock lifted from his expression, he took
 the strange cross between a hairy nut and a fruit in his hands, and drank
 a good mouthful.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
After he had quite thoroughly sloshed it around his mouth in an evident
 display of the juice's potable quality, he swallowed and offered it back
 to Hilderich who accepted it, even though still reluctantly, sniffing the
