\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

It's sweet and refreshing.
 Almost better than water.
 Drink up, you'll like it.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Amonas was motioning with his head for Hilderich to drink, urging him to
 just have a taste, while Hilderich slowly brought the fruit to his lips,
 eyeing Amonas warily at the some time.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
After a brief pause and a small period of uncertainty, Hilderich finally
 took a small sip, swallowed, and then surprising even himself in the process,
 proceeded to empty the small ball of a fruit of its watery content.
