\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

I wouldn't kill you with fruit Hilderich.
 There were ample opportunities with better tools.
 We need to trust each other to make it back, that much I can assure you.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Oh I know about your assurances so far.
 I can see them all around us, sure as hell.
