\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

I'll restrain from further commenting on the problematic issue and instead
 focus on more worthwhile endeavors, such as getting back.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Amonas smiled even as he said in a genuinely friendly tone:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

That's more befitting a Curator now, isn't it?Let me catch some sleep, and
