\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Hilderich was still catching his breath when he said to Amonas in a knowing
 manner:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

It's too hot and too wet for comfort, what else is there to notice?That
